# Screens & Components

Source of truth: @ai/rules/projects/fin-app-mobile/architecture.md
Common React rules: @ai/rules/common/react.md

## Quick Rules

- Every screen/component in its own folder: `FooScreen/FooScreen.tsx`
- All logic in co-located hook: `useFooScreen.ts` — never in JSX
- Component max 150 lines | Hook max 50 lines | JSX nesting max 4 | Props max 7
- NativeWind `className` only — no inline `style={{}}` for layout (only dynamic computed values)
- No hardcoded hex colors — use Tailwind tokens; dark mode via `dark:` prefix
- Amounts: `/100` on load, `Math.round(*100)` on submit; guard `if (!amount) return` before sign flip
- Dates: `toLocaleDateString('uk-UA')`
- No array index as key in FlatList/ScrollView
- No `useEffect` to sync derived state — compute in render
- `useCallback` for handlers passed as props
- Extract repeated JSX (3+) into a component
- Extract `Platform.select` duplication to `src/shared/lib/platform.ts`
